alhost/wordpresseng/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/lion-3576045__480.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-148\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":153,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpresseng/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/adler-2386314__480-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-153\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":150,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpresseng/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/elephant-1822636__480.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-150\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></figure>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Eventually, I managed to get the park owner to put my caf√© in the middle of the park. We decided to put a cafe over the waterfall, hanging it on thick metal chains to. So dangerous predators can‚Äôt reach visitors.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":141,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpresseng/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Vodop-dy-B-l-Opavy-1024x681.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-141\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now people from all over the world come to Prague to enjoy a beautiful view of the waterfall, exotic animals and fish, as well as a hot cup of coffee. That‚Äôs how a little book got me to succeed and made me world famous</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'My story', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-03-25 21:28:42', '2023-03-25 21:28:42', '', 2, 'http://localhost/wordpresseng/?p=155', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
